{"id":247297,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/看厦门商报教你如何ps：青天白日旗变身红旗/","date":"2012-08-16T05:54:27Z","modified":"2012-08-16T06:00:11Z","title":"看厦门商报教你如何PS：青天白日旗变身红旗（更新：已公开道歉）","content":"<p>（点击<a href=\"http://www.xmnn.cn/dzbk/xmsb/epaper/html/2012-08/16/content_396498.htm\">这里查看</a>《厦门商报》电子版原文）</p>\n<p>《厦门商报》今日头版刊登的保钓新闻所使用了修改过的图片。原始照片内的青天白日旗竟被修改成红旗。</p>\n<p><em>【更新】</em>：《厦门商报》已为其头版使用PS掉青天白日旗的事件在网络上公开道歉：</p>\n<blockquote><p>致歉：本报今日不当使用PS图片，伤害了读者的感情。做为负责任的媒体，不应发生这样的错误。在此特向广大读者致歉!</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/08/Screenshot_41.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-247303\" title=\"Screenshot_4\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/08/Screenshot_41.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"569\" height=\"152\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/08/Screenshot_41.jpg 569w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/08/Screenshot_41-300x80.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 569px) 100vw, 569px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/08/3.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-247299\" title=\"3\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/08/3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"585\" height=\"635\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/08/3.jpg 585w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/08/3-276x300.jpg 276w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>以下为原始照片</strong>（来自新浪微博）：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/08/94680c92jw1dvyaq1l1ghj1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-247300\" title=\"94680c92jw1dvyaq1l1ghj\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/08/94680c92jw1dvyaq1l1ghj1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"373\" height=\"476\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/08/94680c92jw1dvyaq1l1ghj1.jpg 373w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/08/94680c92jw1dvyaq1l1ghj1-235x300.jpg 235w\" sizes=\